{
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "11.1",
      "line_index": 11,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7f6995e0",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "おにーさん、なんか疲れてる？　ゆうでよければ相談のろっか？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "13.0",
      "line_index": 13,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "2f3334a8",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゆうが部屋にやってきて、心配そうな顔でこちらを見上げる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "14.0",
      "line_index": 14,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "7f54a1ae",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その瞳には、無邪気な愛らしさと、どこか人を惹きつけるような不思議な魅力が宿っている。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "16.0",
      "line_index": 16,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "cb2d6866",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "あ、ああ……まあ、少しな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "18.0",
      "line_index": 18,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a3ab60e9",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（別に、ゆうに話すようなことでもないし……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "20.1",
      "line_index": 20,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "e4e48a51",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "ふーん？　そっかー。でも、なんか元気ないよー",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "22.1",
      "line_index": 22,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "2c32195e",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "ねえ、もしかして、悩み事？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "24.0",
      "line_index": 24,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "d8a38b69",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "うーん……まあ、ちょっと考え事をしてただけだよ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "26.1",
      "line_index": 26,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "cd5a155d",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "考え事？　どんなことー？　教えられないことー？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "28.0",
      "line_index": 28,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "8b1c7ad2",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "えっと……最近、リリアンのことで色々あってさ……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "30.1",
      "line_index": 30,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "c35cda2f",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "リリアン？　あ……ひょっとして、近くの星の……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "32.0",
      "line_index": 32,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a00f2c78",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "え、どうしてゆうが……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "34.1",
      "line_index": 34,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "a51e8ece",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "ゆう、こっちのことも知りたくて、いっぱいみんなとお話ししたんだー",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "36.1",
      "line_index": 36,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "bebc014f",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "でも……楽しいことばっかじゃなくて、辛いこともあるんだよね……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "38.0",
      "line_index": 38,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "fa68a7fd",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そう。リリアンへの差別がひどすぎると思って……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "40.1",
      "line_index": 40,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "8229efba",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "さべつ？　そんなのだめ！　なんでそんなことしちゃうのー！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "42.0",
      "line_index": 42,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9fd3d9f8",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "みんな同じ人間なのに、あんなに酷い扱いを受けて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "44.1",
      "line_index": 44,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "4b2360ca",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "うう……おにーさんは、そのことが辛いの……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "46.0",
      "line_index": 46,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "bb638d39",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "俺は……何も、できないのが口惜しくて……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "48.1",
      "line_index": 48,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "d4f09f4d",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "それでずっと考えてるんだ",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "50.0",
      "line_index": 50,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "a5d19da6",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "う、うん……何か支援できることがないかって、ずっと考えてる……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "52.1",
      "line_index": 52,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "ea42ee91",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "そっかー。おにーさん、ほんとに優しいんだねー",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "54.0",
      "line_index": 54,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "72bb675f",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "そんなこと……",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "56.1",
      "line_index": 56,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "962223ea",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "でも、一人で抱え込まないで、ゆうにもっと頼ってよー？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "58.0",
      "line_index": 58,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9156345d",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "ゆうに、か……？",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "60.1",
      "line_index": 60,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "960b534a",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "そうだよー。ゆうは、おにーさんの味方だからね！",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "62.0",
      "line_index": 62,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "1cac1685",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゆうが抱き着いてきて、頭を撫でてくれる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "63.0",
      "line_index": 63,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "739cfb83",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その小さな体温が、疲れた心にじんわりと染み込んでいく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "65.1",
      "line_index": 65,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "5e384037",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "よしよし、おにーさん。大丈夫だよー",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "67.0",
      "line_index": 67,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f4f78675",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゆうは優しく背中をさすり、囁くように慰めてくれる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "69.1",
      "line_index": 69,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "aa676710",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "ゆうがついてるから、なんでも話してね",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "71.0",
      "line_index": 71,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "9d3dba40",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゆうの長い黒髪が頬にかかり、くすぐったい。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "72.0",
      "line_index": 72,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "5a2b3f66",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "同時に、甘くて優しい香りが鼻をくすぐる。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "73.0",
      "line_index": 73,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "ffa7b354",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その香りは、まるで幼い頃に嗅いだことのある、安心できる匂い。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "75.0",
      "line_index": 75,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "3a15911",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（あー……だめなのに、こんな年下の女の子に慰めてもらって、優しくしてもらうなんて……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "77.0",
      "line_index": 77,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6f029b18",
      "speaker": "{G_PlayerName}",
      "ja": "（でも……心地いい……）",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "79.0",
      "line_index": 79,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "f2b084d5",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "されるがままに、ゆうに身を委ねてしまう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "80.0",
      "line_index": 80,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "50d03bc0",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "ゆうの甘い香りと温もりに包まれ、心が安らいでいく。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "82.1",
      "line_index": 82,
      "inline_index": 1,
      "line_hash": "7efb3681",
      "speaker": "ゆう",
      "ja": "おにーさんの辛いこと、全部ゆうが無くしてあげたいな",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "84.0",
      "line_index": 84,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "204150e7",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "俺を見下ろしながらにっこりと笑うゆう。",
      "zh": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "85.0",
      "line_index": 85,
      "inline_index": 0,
      "line_hash": "6957e48",
      "speaker": "",
      "ja": "その姿は、まるで本当の妹のように愛らしい。",
      "zh": ""
    }
  ]
}
